  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_1",
    "text": "附子",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.4738858626273595,
      0.14306152299540886,
      0.5444646081250513,
      0.16009265668533848
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_2",
    "text": "【来源】毛茛科植物乌头的子根的加工品。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15880217736980662,
      0.16690511016131032,
      0.49405121848384287,
      0.18393624385123994
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_6",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5772333113918368,
      0.17031133689929626,
      0.8948376661314501,
      0.3218884267396699
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_3",
    "text": "【采收加工】夏秋季采挖，除去主根、须根及泥 沙，习称“泥附子”。以不同的方法加工制成盐附 子、黑顺片、白附片直接入药。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1209921351389003,
      0.18734247058922587,
      0.5570679555353534,
      0.2452483251349866
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_4",
    "text": "【质量标志】盐附子以个大、体重、色灰黄、表 面起盐霜者为佳。黑顺片以片大、厚薄均匀、切面油 润有光泽者为佳。白附片以片大、色白、油润、半透 明者为佳。水分不得超过15%。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1209921351389003,
      0.24865455187297253,
      0.5570679555353534,
      0.3269977668466488
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_5",
    "text": "【饮片特征】①盐附子：呈圆锥形，顶端凹陷， 福",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13863682151332324,
      0.33040399358463474,
      0.5495059470891721,
      0.3474351272745643
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_7",
    "text": "高5～8cm。表面黑褐色，粗糙，附有盐粒结晶，可见突起的支根及支根痕，断面色略淡，有 1个多角形环纹。体重，质稍坚。气微，味咸而麻舌。②黑顺片（图2-168）：为纵切片，上宽 下窄，长1.7~5cm，宽0.9～3cm，厚0.2~0.5cm。外皮黑褐色，切面暗黄色，油润且具光 泽，呈半透明状，并有纵向导管束。质硬而脆，断面呈角质样。气微，味淡。③白附片：无残留 外皮，呈黄白色，半透明，厚约0.3 cm。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1209921351389003,
      0.3508413540125503,
      0.899879005095571,
      0.4496219294141421
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_8",
    "text": "【贮藏要求】置干燥处，防潮。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15880217736980662,
      0.45302815615212805,
      0.4033071171296676,
      0.47005928984205764
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_9",
    "text": "肉桂",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.4764065321094199,
      0.4802779700560154,
      0.5444646081250513,
      0.49730910374594506
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_10",
    "text": "【来源】樟科植物肉桂的树皮。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15880217736980662,
      0.5041215572219169,
      0.4007864476476072,
      0.5211526909118466
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_15",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5747126419097763,
      0.5092308973288958,
      0.8973583356135105,
      0.6608079871692695
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_11",
    "text": "【采收加工】一般在秋季剥取，阴干。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15880217736980662,
      0.5245589176498324,
      0.45876184573499695,
      0.5415900513397621
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_12",
    "text": "【质量标志】药材以皮细而坚实，肉厚而沉重， 断面紫红色，油性足，香气浓，辛、甜味大，嚼之无 渣者为佳。水分不得超过15%，总灰分不得超过5%。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1209921351389003,
      0.544996278077748,
      0.5570679555353534,
      0.6029021326235087
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_13",
    "text": "【饮片特征】呈不规则的板状或卷筒状，厚 0.2～0.8cm。外表面呈灰棕色，有的可见灰白色斑 纹。内表面呈红棕色，较平坦，有细纵纹，划处显油 痕。质硬，断面不平坦，外层呈棕色、较粗糙，内 层呈红棕色，有油润感，两层间可见1条黄棕色的线 纹。气香浓烈，味甜、辣。（图2-169)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1209921351389003,
      0.6063083593614946,
      0.5595886250174138,
      0.725526295191002
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_14",
    "text": "【贮藏要求】置阴凉且干燥处。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15880217736980662,
      0.7323387486669739,
      0.4033071171296676,
      0.7493698823569035
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_16",
    "text": "干姜",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.4764065321094199,
      0.7578854492018683,
      0.5444646081250513,
      0.774916582891798
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_17",
    "text": "【来源】姜科植物姜的根茎。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.15880217736980662,
      0.7834321497367628,
      0.3831417612731842,
      0.7987601700576994
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129_18",
    "text": "【采收加工】冬季采收，去掉须根和泥沙，晒干或者低温干燥。趁鲜进行切片晒干或低温干 燥者称为“干姜”。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11595079617477945,
      0.8038695101646783,
      0.899879005095571,
      0.8396348909135305
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61570552.pdf_129",
    "order": 19
  }
]